The Debian package description
.INDENT 7.0
.IP \(bu 2
Mandatory : YES
.IP \(bu 2
Default   :
.INDENT 2.0
.IP \(bu 2
\fI\%CPACK_DEBIAN_PACKAGE_DESCRIPTION\fP if set or
