.TP
.B cpack_ifw_add_package_resources
Add additional resources in the installer binary.
.INDENT 7.0
.INDENT 3.5
.sp
.nf
.ft C
cpack_ifw_add_package_resources(<file_path> <file_path> ...)
.ft P
.fi
.UNINDENT
.UNINDENT
